    },
    {
      "text": "Cool World is an action video game developed by British studio Painting By Numbers. It was released by Ocean Software in 1993 for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It is loosely based on the 1992 movie of the same name. Both the European and North American versions are in English.\nIn contrast to the computer/Game Boy and NES versions, this version of the game plays more like an adventure game. It is the only version of the game that allows players to control Jack Deebs, who must avoid the advances of Holli Would and return home.\nCool World was first mentioned in issue #47 (April 1993) of the North American video gaming magazine Nintendo Power.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Cool World è un videogioco a piattaforme e picchiaduro del 1993 tratto dal film Fuga dal mondo dei sogni (1992) e pubblicato per console Super Nintendo Entertainment System dalla Ocean Software.\nIl protagonista Frank Harris deve attraversare diversi luoghi a scorrimento multidirezionale, affrontando armato di un pugno allungabile i bizzarri personaggi-cartoni animati detti Doodle. Il pugno può servire anche ad aggrapparsi a piattaforme e sollevarsi. Alcuni brevi livelli sono alla guida di un veicolo.\nL'azienda pubblicò anche Cool World (1992) per computer e Cool World (1993) per NES, i quali, sebbene abbiano la stessa ambientazione e copertina molto simile, sono giochi piuttosto differenti.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『クール・ワールド』は、イギリスのスタジオ「Painting By Numbers」が開発したアクションビデオゲームです。1993年にオーシャン・ソフトウェアからスーパーファミコン向けに発売されました。本作は、同名の1992年の映画をモチーフにしています。欧州版と北米版の両方とも英語仕様です。\n\nコンピューター/ゲームボーイ版やNES版とは異なり、このバージョンはアドベンチャーゲームに近いゲームプレイが特徴です。プレイヤーは、ホリー・ウッドの誘惑を避け、帰宅しなければならないジャック・ディーブスを操作できる唯一のバージョンでもあります。\n\n『クール・ワールド』は、北米のビデオゲーム雑誌『ニンテンドー・パワー』の第47号（1993年4月号）で初めて言及されました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
